查普尔·罗恩说成名就像“一个虐待他的前夫” https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chappell-roan-says-fame-就像一个有虐待倾向的前夫Laura MolloyTue, 17 Sep 2024 20:05:26 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3794622 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="查普尔·罗恩.图片来源：Dana Jacobs/WireImage" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不知道感觉会这么糟糕。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622">查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 称成名就像“有虐待倾向的前夫”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="查普尔·罗恩.图片来源：Dana Jacobs/WireImage" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>在一次新的采访中表示，名气的影响就像与“虐待性的前夫”打交道。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">Chappell Roan：流行超新星，感觉就像“变装皇后”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>近几个月来，罗恩一直直言不讳地讲述了她的成名经历。她最近在 TikTok 上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">分享了她对“奇怪”和“令人毛骨悚然”的粉丝行为的看法</a>，质疑为什么人们觉得他们可以在车里对她大喊大叫，因为她拒绝拍照而生她的气，跟踪她或以其他方式骚扰她因为她的名人地位。</p><p>她后来说，骚扰“对于名人或小名气的人来说是很正常的事情”，但“这并不意味着它就可以”或“正常”。</p><p>现在，罗恩表示她觉得名声是“虐待”。在接受<a href="https://theface.com/music/chappell-roan-pop-music-famous-interview-good-luck-babe"><em>The Face</em></a>的一次新采访中，这位歌手将这段经历比作与“虐待前夫”打交道，她说：“这种氛围——跟踪、在网上说废话、[人]不会让你孤单、大喊大叫在公共场合对你——有一种虐待前夫的感觉。就是这样的感觉。我不知道这种感觉会这么糟糕。” </p><figure id="attachment_3793242" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793242" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793242" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-@-2000-x-1270-Udo-Salters_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 出席 2024 年 MTV VMA 颁奖典礼。图片来源：Udo Salters/Patrick McMullan，来自 Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-@-2000-x-1270-Udo-Salters_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-@-2000-x-1270-Udo-Salters_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-@-2000-x-1270-Udo-Salters_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-@-2000-x-1270-Udo-Salters_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-@-2000-x-1270-Udo-Salters_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-@-2000-x-1270-Udo-Salters_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793242" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 出席 2024 年 MTV VMA 颁奖典礼。图片来源：Udo Salters/Patrick McMullan，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在解释她的评论时，罗恩回忆起最近的一次经历，当时她早上 5 点 30 分到达机场，“两个人拿着一堆海报和狗屎等着我签名”。</p><p> â�&lt;“我知道他们不是粉丝，”她解释道。 “我说不。我当时想，“抱歉，我没有在机场签署任何东西。” [其中一个]跟着我到 TSA 排队，开始对我大喊大叫，每个人都转过身来看着。他说：“你真的应该谦虚一点。”你知道你现在在哪里吗？不要忘记你从哪里来。”我只是想：“这到底是怎么回事？”我告诉自己，如果这变得危险，我可能会退出。现在很危险，但我还是要走。但这部分不是我签约的。”</p><p>她还透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">洛德</a>主动<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-lorde-sent-her-a-list-of-ways-to-cope-with-negativity-and-fame-3794353">分享了她年轻时应对名声和消极情绪的经历</a>。 “她给我发了一份我应该做的事情清单，”罗恩说。 “从字面上写下了八件事，她希望有人在她经历这件事时告诉她。她经历了该死的地狱。她还是个婴儿！”</p><p>在她对粉丝行为发表评论后，众多音乐界大腕向这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">前<em>NME 封面</em>明星</a>伸出援手，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">Katy Perry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">MUNA</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">boygenius</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mitski">Mitski</a> 。</p><p>在罗恩向粉丝们发布视频之前，她曾表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-shes-pumped-the-brakes-on-fame-after-fans-give-off-stalker-vibes-3775922">，在粉丝们散发出“跟踪者的氛围”后，她想“踩刹车”她的职业生涯</a>。她的言论赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Paramore">Paramore</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/aritsts/Hayley-Williams">Hayley Williams</a>的赞扬，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramores-hayley-williams-supports-chappell-roans-brave-and-unfortunately-necessary-boundary-comments-3787404">在 Instagram 上称赞这位流行歌星“勇敢”</a> 。</p><p>上周在 MTV VMA 的其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-snaps-back-at-vmas-photographer-who-seemingly-told-her-to-shut-the-fuck-up-3792891">罗恩回击了一位摄影师，后者似乎告诉她在红地毯上“他妈的闭嘴”</a> 。在颁奖典礼之前，这位冉冉升起的流行歌星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappel-roan-cancels-number-of-european-shows-due-to-scheduling-conflicts-3788740">因“日程安排冲突”而取消了两场欧洲演出，</a>遭到了一些强烈反对。随后她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-fans-react-after-she-posts-vma-rehearsal-photos-ahead-of-cancelled-gigs-3790886">发布了自己在 VMA 排练中的照片</a>。</p><p>去年九月，罗恩发行了她的首张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">中西部公主的兴衰</a>》，广受好评。 <em>《NME》</em>在一篇<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">四星评论</a>中将其描述为“罗恩大胆而厚颜无耻的笔的展示，她在其中将灼热的启示与一些可爱的厚颜无耻的合唱一起放置”。</p><p>发行近一年后，这张专辑就登上了英国专辑排行榜的榜首—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-congratulates-chappell-roan-on-chart-success-the-meteoric-rise-of-a-midwestern-princess-3782611">艾尔顿·约翰对此表示祝贺</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 称成名就像“虐待性的前夫”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
